Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,, forgetted根据BDRip TLF版本重新调整字幕\N豆瓣@LoudCrazyHeart调整时间轴 适配The.Fog.1980.REMASTERED.720p.BluRay.X264-AMIABLE版本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“所见非见，亦梦亦幻” ---- 埃德加·爱伦·坡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,11 :55.\N{\fs14}11 :55.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快到午夜了.\N{\fs14}Almost midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,时间还够讲个故事的.\N{\fs14}Enough time for one more story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,讲个12:00前能结束的故事...\N{\fs14}One more story before 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来给我们增加点暖气儿.\N{\fs14}just to keep us warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再过五分钟，就是4月21号了.\N{\fs14}ln five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是4月21号了.\N{\fs14}it'll be the 21st of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一百年前，也是4月21号...\N{\fs14}One hundred years ago on the 21st of April,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在Spivey Point周围的水域...\N{\fs14}out in the waters around Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘快速帆船靠岸了.\N{\fs14}a small clipper ship drew toward land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间，夜色冥冥中，\N{\fs14}Suddenly, out of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一场大雾降临了.\N{\fs14}the fog rolled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一瞬间，他们什么也看不清...\N{\fs14}For a moment, they could see nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,即使眼前一英尺的距离都看不清.\N{\fs14}not a foot ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这时他们看到了一柱火光.\N{\fs14}And then, they saw a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝呀，是海滩上的一团火...\N{\fs14}My God, it was a fire burning on the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那火光很强，足以穿透厚重的迷雾.\N{\fs14}Strong enough to penetrate the swirling mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他们转舵驶向火光...\N{\fs14}They steered a course toward the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但那仅仅是堆篝火，就像这个一样.\N{\fs14}But it was a campfire, like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帆船撞上了礁石.\N{\fs14}The ship crashed against the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,船体被撞成两半.\N{\fs14}The hull sheared in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,桅杆像树枝一样断裂...\N{\fs14}The mast snapped like a twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这场海难把全船人都葬身大海.\N{\fs14}And the wreckage sank with all the men aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在深深的海底...\N{\fs14}At the bottom of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沉睡着''伊丽莎白.丹恩''号，和她的船员们...\N{\fs14}lay the Elizabeth Dane with her crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的肺里灌满了咸咸的海水...\N{\fs14}their lungs filled with saltwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的眼睛大睁着，直盯入黑暗中.\N{\fs14}their eyes open and staring into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切发生之后，那雾一如来时的突然...\N{\fs14}And above, as suddenly as it had come,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然升高了... 然后慢慢的消失在大洋彼岸...\N{\fs14}the fog lifted, receded back across the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没有来过.\N{\fs14}and never came again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一件事却被渔夫们...\N{\fs14}But it is told by the fishermen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他们的爸爸们、爷爷们，一直传说至今...\N{\fs14}and their fathers and grandfathers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是，据说有一天，当那场大雾再次回到安东尼湾的时候...\N{\fs14}that when the fog returns to Antonio Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沉睡在Spivey Point周围水域...\N{\fs14}the men at the bottom of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,海底的那些人们...\N{\fs14}out in the water by Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,会再次醒来\N{\fs14}will rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找那堆火\N{\fs14}and search for the campfire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是那堆火，把他们引向了黑暗而冰冷的死亡.\N{\fs14}that led them to their dark, icy death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,12点.\N{\fs14}Twelve o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,4月21号\N{\fs14}The 21st of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻是午夜12点,我们开始进入午夜时段的播音.\N{\fs14}It's midnight and we've just started into the witching hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史蒂芙.韦恩，今夜唯我独在.\N{\fs14}This is Stevie Wayne, on top of the world tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会与您相伴在此，直到1:00点钟左右.\N{\fs14}and I'II be here right up untiI about one o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我完成了，神父.\N{\fs14}l'm all through, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，谢谢你，班尼特.\N{\fs14}Oh, thank you, Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明早4点之前，你不用来了，班尼特\N{\fs14}l won't need you until four tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的.\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来点？回家路上能暖和些。\N{\fs14}Something to keep you warm on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不了，谢谢。 神父，我能把薪水领了么？\N{\fs14}No, thank you. Father, can l get paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就明早6点钟过来好吧？4点钟不用来了.\N{\fs14}Why don't you come in at six instead of four tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的.\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,班尼特?\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,户外温度59度.\N{\fs14}It's 59 degrees outside
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,让我成为第一个祝福安东尼湾的人 生日快乐.\N{\fs14}and Iet me be the first to wish Antonio Bay a happy birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今天，我们已经整整一百岁了.\N{\fs14}We're 100 years oId today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,气象预报员差点搅了我们的兴致.\N{\fs14}The weatherman's trying to spoiI it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他说今晚可能会有降雨.\N{\fs14}He says we may be in for rain tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是从我所处的位置看来，天空依然清朗.\N{\fs14}From where I'm sitting, it Iooks Iike cIear skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想，也许是气象员工作的太劳累了吧.\N{\fs14}I think the weatherman's been working too hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我会在这里再待上一小时, 来验证一下他是否正确.\N{\fs14}WeII, I'II stay here for another hour, just to see if he's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,并且我也邀请您和我一起共度.\N{\fs14}And I'm inviting you to stay here with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,东部海湾附近，有一云层断带，完毕.\N{\fs14}There's a cutter run aground over here on the east bay, Over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,定位 1X5. 是"平静的贝丽女士".\N{\fs14}GIobaI 1 X, This cutter's name's Lady BeIIe Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,序号024KL596. 完毕.\N{\fs14}SeriaI number 024KL596, Over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,定位 1X5. "平静的贝丽女士"... 适于航行, 无显著危险.\N{\fs14}GIobaI 1 X5, Lady BeIIe Pacific is seaworthy, No major damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请求派出一艘拖船来 大约在Boatel前方1/4海里处. 完毕.\N{\fs14}Why don't you send a tow, I'm about a quarter miIe above the boateI, Over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是KAB电台, 在加利福尼亚的安东尼湾向您播报.\N{\fs14}This is KAB, Antonio Bay, CaIifornia,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,刚过午夜6分钟.\N{\fs14}Six minutes after midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,气象预报员还没传送过来消息 所以我不能断言关于来雨的信息\N{\fs14}Haven't heard from the weatherman, so I don't know about that rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但可以看到满月当空, 万里无云.\N{\fs14}But there's a fuII moon and no cIouds in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是史蒂芙.韦恩. 如果您此刻恰巧无事可做\N{\fs14}I'm Stevie Wayne and if you don't have anything to do right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我会在这午夜一小时当中, 为您播放动听的音乐.\N{\fs14}I'II be here, pIaying music, aII through the witching hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,即使您有事可做 也再多开一会儿收音机\N{\fs14}Even if you do have something to do, keep me turned on for a whiIe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也会尽力有事可做, 为了您.\N{\fs14}and I'II try my best to do the same for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好!\N{\fs14}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要走多远？\N{\fs14}Hi. How far you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-去镇那边. 嗯，足够近了.\N{\fs14}- Other side of town. - Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-能行吧？ -行的，谢谢你。\N{\fs14}- Can you make it? - Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝么？\N{\fs14}Sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说，我此前从没搭过便车.\N{\fs14}Listen, l never hitchhiked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想小心翼翼些.\N{\fs14}l just really wanna be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能问你个问题吗？ -可以.\N{\fs14}- Can l ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人怪吗？\N{\fs14}Are you weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我很怪.\N{\fs14}Yes, l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那好，我也很怪. 你很怪异.\N{\fs14}- l am weird. - You are weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝.感谢上帝你也很怪. 上一个我搭过车的人，就很正常，太讨厌了.\N{\fs14}Thank God. The last one l had was so normal it was disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他在圣芭芭拉让我搭的车. 等我们到卡梅尔的时候，他就要我嫁给他.\N{\fs14}He picked me up in Santa Barbara. By Carmel, he wanted to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，明白了. 我相信你“此前从未搭过便车”.\N{\fs14}Yeah. l thought you never hitchhiked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,上周以来没搭过.\N{\fs14}Not before last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的第十三次搭车.\N{\fs14}You're my thirteenth ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，好极了. 怪异又不幸.\N{\fs14}Great. Weird and unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧.\N{\fs14}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事儿吧？ -我还好.\N{\fs14}- Are you all right? You sure? - l'm fine. l think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么该死的--\N{\fs14}What the hell was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜过后整12分钟了 这里是史蒂芙.韦恩.\N{\fs14}It's tweIve minutes after midnight and this is Stevie Wayne,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,走，离开这里. 我会伴你至 1点\N{\fs14}- Let's get out of here. - Around untiI about 1 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我在Spivey Point高高的KAB灯塔上.\N{\fs14}I'm high tonight in the KAB Iighthouse on Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也许您忘记了，今天是4月21日\N{\fs14}In case you've forgotten, it's ApriI 21st
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是安东尼湾的美好生日.\N{\fs14}and a happy birthday for Antonio Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，有一场庆典正在筹备中.\N{\fs14}There's a celebration planned for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，如果您为此兴奋的睡不着觉\N{\fs14}So if you're so excited about it you can't sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，起来和我一起吧\N{\fs14}well, stay up with me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想出办法来的，不会让您闲着.\N{\fs14}and l'll figure out some way to keep you occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,或者，让您悠闲着.\N{\fs14}Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- KAB. -嗨，甜心.\N{\fs14}- KAB. - Hi, sweetheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，丹. 有什么想说的？\N{\fs14}Hi, Dan, what have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你孤单吗？ 看看我能不能为你做点什么.\N{\fs14}Are you lonely? ls there anything l can do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不孤单 我记得你8:00就下班了呀.\N{\fs14}Never IoneIy, I thought you finished at eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我换班了，以便参加今晚的聚会庆典.\N{\fs14}l changed shifts so l can make it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你会去吗？\N{\fs14}Will you be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我能说服某个人 放弃美妙的城市夜生活来安东尼湾度过，就像我这样.\N{\fs14}Until l can talk someone into giving up city life for Antonio Bay, l'm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-而“这样”指的是一天一宿. -你工作太忙了.\N{\fs14}- And it means day and night. - Too much work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓岗位的意义.\N{\fs14}That's what l get for owning a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你15秒钟内还不告诉我为什么打来 我就不得不挂断你了.\N{\fs14}Tell me why you called, or in 15 seconds l'm gonna hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-想听我说什么吗？ -你随意.\N{\fs14}- You want something to talk about? - Anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我观测到一艘拖船 大约15海里外\N{\fs14}l've got a position on a trawler about 15 miles out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,名字叫做“海草”.\N{\fs14}called the Sea Grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,并且我在望远镜里看到些东西-- 看起来像是个雾带.\N{\fs14}l've got something on my scope - appears to be a fog bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在大约25海里外，正朝拖船方向移动.\N{\fs14}lt's about 25 miles out and moving in their direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢，丹. 这段话值上10秒钟了.\N{\fs14}Thanks. That's worth about ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在电波中. 再见.\N{\fs14}I'm on the air, Bye,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的朋友.这里是安东尼湾的KAB电台.\N{\fs14}Ahoy, mateys. This is KAB, Antonio Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芙.韦恩在此向您播报关于海上的一个讯息.\N{\fs14}Stevie Wayne here, beaming a signal across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请“海草”号船员注意 大约15海里外，今晚\N{\fs14}For the men in the Sea Grass, 1 5 miIes out tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有个“热情的招呼”在等待他们 所以请保持观察，密切注意那个雾带\N{\fs14}a warm heIIo and keep a watch out for that fog bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,从东面移动过来.\N{\fs14}heading in from the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，那么此刻,请跟随我播放的这首歌曲\N{\fs14}In the meantime, reIax with me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,轻松一下 来自于Coupe DeVilles的歌\N{\fs14}whiIe I pIay this song from the Coupe De ViIIes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,特意为你们点播的.\N{\fs14}dedicated just to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小子，我真想见到她.\N{\fs14}Boy, would l like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一次在百货店里见到她. 你肯定想见到她的.\N{\fs14}l saw her at a grocery store. You would like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她很令人疯狂. 那里没有雾带呀.\N{\fs14}She's crazy. There's no fog bank out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关于她你还知道什么？ -那座灯塔是属于她的.\N{\fs14}- What do you know about her? - She owns that lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-这我知道. 她儿子和我的小弟弟在一起结伴玩.\N{\fs14}- l know. - Her son plays little league.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她当妈了？ 我以为你的婚姻挺幸福了呢.\N{\fs14}- She's a mother? - l thought you were happily married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么幸福. 那边确实没有雾带.\N{\fs14}- Not that happy. - No fog bank out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那边确实有个雾带.\N{\fs14}There's a fog bank out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了. 我喝的够多了.咱们回舱吧.\N{\fs14}All right. l'm drunk enough. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，好的.\N{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔，过来.\N{\fs14}Al, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-帮我个忙. -过来.\N{\fs14}- Just give him a hand. - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?\N{\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来看.\N{\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fs14}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是蒸汽机.\N{\fs14}lt's a generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了.刚才有艘船在那里的.\N{\fs14}lt's gone. There was just a ship out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听\N{\fs14}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有. -听.\N{\fs14}- Nothing. - Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁在那儿？\N{\fs14}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁？\N{\fs14}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我们旁边.\N{\fs14}lt's right beside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀，艾尔. 是一艘船.\N{\fs14}lt's big, Al. lt's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是一艘大船.\N{\fs14}lt's a big ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？你怎么弄湿了？\N{\fs14}What happened? You get wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,12点43分\N{\fs14}lt's 12:43
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在此为您准备了四首曲目\N{\fs14}and l've got four in a row for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,KAB播音电台.\N{\fs14}right here on KAB.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,除了水什么也没有，史蒂芙.\N{\fs14}Nothing but water, Stevie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但确实到达了芝加哥海岸.\N{\fs14}But it sure beats Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,KAB.\N{\fs14}KAB.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你说的话 但是给你个信息：你说谎了.\N{\fs14}l like what you said but for your information, you lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雾带向西移去 而且可能和拖船完全交错而过.\N{\fs14}The fog bank has moved due west and probably missed the ship entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，我的仪器一定出错了. 我测到有向东刮的风.\N{\fs14}My gauges must be wrong. l've got a wind blowing due east.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么雾会逆风而飘呢？\N{\fs14}What kind of a fog moves against the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-你得到我了. -我可不确定是否想要你.\N{\fs14}- You got me, - l'm not so sure l want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是电话中的一个声音而已. 你是电话中的一个声音.\N{\fs14}- You're just a voice on the phone. - You're just a voice on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以是完美的一对儿.\N{\fs14}We'd make a perfect coupIe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你允许我今晚带你去参加晚宴， 我就会证明给你看.\N{\fs14}You Iet me take you to dinner tonight, I'II prove it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉，丹. 我认为最完美的就仅止于电话中的一个声音.\N{\fs14}Sorry, Dan. My idea of perfection is a voice on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，神秘的女士.\N{\fs14}OK, mystery Iady,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安.\N{\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还不坏.\N{\fs14}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一周前我从圣地亚哥出发\N{\fs14}l started a week ago in San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着海岸线，每天画五幅画.\N{\fs14}Right up the coast, five drawings a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会用上一个月才能到达温哥华 如果我能每张画卖5块钱,我就有钱了.\N{\fs14}lt'll take a month to get to Vancouver but if l sell them for five bucks apiece, l'll be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能问你点事儿吗？ -问吧.\N{\fs14}- Can l ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-伊丽莎白. -尼克.\N{\fs14}- Elizabeth. - Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好，尼克.\N{\fs14}Hello, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好\N{\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是从那里来的吗？圣地亚哥？\N{\fs14}ls that where you're from, San Diego?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了，“我能问你点事儿吗？”\N{\fs14}You said, ''Can l ask you something?''
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那么点事儿，对我而言，就是指一件事. -加上圣地亚哥是两件事儿了.\N{\fs14}Something, to me, means one thing. San Diego is two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是Pasadena\N{\fs14}Pasadena
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大把的钱.\N{\fs14}and a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有机会让我做我想做的事.\N{\fs14}And never a chance to do anything l wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么？\N{\fs14}What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道.\N{\fs14}l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行了. 我也一样.\N{\fs14}That's OK. Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要这个. 我能买下它吗？\N{\fs14}l think l gotta have this one. Can l buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这画是免费的.\N{\fs14}The drawing's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一点整了\N{\fs14}It's one o'clock, straight up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.61,0:24:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜一小时结束之际，也是我将要告别之时.\N{\fs14}The end of the witching hour and time for me to sign off,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.95,0:24:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,直到明晚六点 KAB再次播音的时候\N{\fs14}So untiI tomorrow night at 6pm, when KAB comes back on the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.62,0:24:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是史蒂芙.韦恩，您的夜空之灯\N{\fs14}this is Stevie Wayne, your night-Iight,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,希望您今夜恬然安适\N{\fs14}hoping you have a nice rest of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.50,0:26:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈!\N{\fs14}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，妈妈!\N{\fs14}Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.39,0:27:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈，快点. 快起来. 看我发现了什么.\N{\fs14}Mom, come on, get up. Look what l found.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.68,0:27:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪\N{\fs14}Andy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.02,0:27:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs14}l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.31,0:27:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时你也真是让人头疼.\N{\fs14}Sometimes you're a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.44,0:27:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，妈妈，可是你看呀.\N{\fs14}Sure, Mom, but look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.28,0:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始，它是一块金币. 然后它就变成了这块光滑木片.\N{\fs14}First it was a gold coin and then it turned into this neat piece of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.53,0:27:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定是过去某个时代的. 你看呀，妈妈.\N{\fs14}- This is one of those times. - But look at it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好，安德鲁. 昨晚过的高兴吗？\N{\fs14}Good morning, Andrew. Did you have a nice time last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.04,0:27:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的. 马谢老爷爷给我们讲鬼故事了.\N{\fs14}Yeah. Old Mr Machen told us ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.09,0:27:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,科布利兹夫人送你回家，你感谢她了吗？\N{\fs14}Did you thank Mrs Kobritz for bringing you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.05,0:27:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官. 妈妈，我能做健身运动然后喝瓶可乐吗？\N{\fs14}Yes, ma'am. Mom, can l have a stomach pounder and a Coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.64,0:27:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-那要午饭后. - OK.\N{\fs14}- After lunch. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.89,0:27:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再去找一片. 也许这次我能捡到金币呢.\N{\fs14}l'm gonna look for another one. Maybe this time l can get the gold coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.13,0:28:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底哪去了？ 昨下午4:15离开的这里.\N{\fs14}- Where the hell is he? - Pulled out of here 4:15 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.63,0:28:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是我最后见到他. -艾尔说7:30，在这儿见.\N{\fs14}- That's the last l saw of him. - l said 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.13,0:28:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道艾尔. 如果我是你-- 你给海岸警卫队打电话了吗，汉克？\N{\fs14}- You know Al. lf l were... - Did you call the coastguard, Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.10,0:28:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可能他们是昨晚喝醉了. 他不会的.\N{\fs14}- They probably got drunk. - He wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.48,0:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-他什么都会. 艾尔和我喝醉多次了\N{\fs14}- He'd do anything. - Al and l got drunk together a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.27,0:28:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们从未如此狼狈过，这次不同往常.\N{\fs14}but we never got so shitfaced we couldn't make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好水手，可以整夜在海上不归 而且不让别人知道.\N{\fs14}He's too good a sailor to stay out and not let somebody know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.61,0:28:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-听起来你像他的老婆. -仅仅是朋友.\N{\fs14}- You sound like his wife. - Just his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-你过于担心了\N{\fs14}You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.08,0:28:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪儿？\N{\fs14}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.08,0:28:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找阿什克罗夫特，谈谈借他的船用用 然后去找“海草”号.\N{\fs14}l'm going to talk Ashcroft into looking for the Sea Grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.50,0:28:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,阿什克罗夫特是谁？ 一个家伙，他欠我人情.\N{\fs14}- Who's Ashcroft? - Someone who owes me a favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.96,0:28:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以一起去吗？\N{\fs14}Can l come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.22,0:28:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你必须要去温哥华的？\N{\fs14}Thought you had to move on to Vancouver?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.55,0:28:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最终会去.\N{\fs14}Eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.15,0:29:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,郡长会开他自己的车来. .\N{\fs14}Sheriff will drive his own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.31,0:29:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,市长及夫人会在6:45被接来\N{\fs14}The Mayor and his wife are to be picked up at 6:45
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.19,0:29:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,并被送到市长专用房间.\N{\fs14}and brought to the Mayor's box.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.19,0:29:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将依次开始讲话，市长，郡长，还有我.\N{\fs14}Then we will have speeches by the Mayor, Sheriff, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你都记下来了吗？\N{\fs14}Do you have my notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.66,0:29:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们要熄灭所有的蜡烛 然后开始节日游行.\N{\fs14}Then we pass out the candles and begin the procession.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.33,0:29:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我回家，再出来.\N{\fs14}Then l will go home and pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.83,0:29:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我都有些不敢看呢.\N{\fs14}l'm almost afraid to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.13,0:29:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好吧...\N{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.85,0:29:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不错. 相当不错. 艺术之作.\N{\fs14}- Not bad. Not bad at all. - A work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,珊蒂，再给我五小时的礼貌相待，如何？ 我就要求这些.\N{\fs14}Sandy, just be civil to me for another five hours, that's all l ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.78,0:29:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来看看.你订了蜡烛没？ 什么意思\N{\fs14}Let's see. Did you order the candles? What a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.32,0:29:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,烛光游行却没有蜡烛？ 都搞定了.\N{\fs14}- A candlelight procession with no candles. - Taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.12,0:29:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再说进一步的准备--你给史蒂芙准备了吗？ 已签好字，已封好，已邮递出去了.\N{\fs14}- And the promotional material, did you...? - Signed, sealed and delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.46,0:29:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有时你可真令人讨厌 但你还就是能和我在一起.\N{\fs14}You can be very annoying but you do keep me together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.83,0:29:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖，威廉夫人.\N{\fs14}Thank you, Mrs Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,此时\N{\fs14},,Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.60,0:30:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,1:57\N{\fs14}As of 1:57 today,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.98,0:30:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“海草”号还是没有回音传回到 无线电通信台.\N{\fs14}the Sea Grass has not responded to radio communication,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.99,0:30:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队已经从Watley南部开始搜寻\N{\fs14}The coastguard has begun a sweep south from WhateIy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在Arcom Reef区域\N{\fs14}around Arcom Reef,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.32,0:30:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能进入Spivey Point区域 约在一小时内到达.\N{\fs14}and shouId be in the area of Spivey Point in approximateIy one hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.08,0:30:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,重复这个播报，来自海岸警卫队的消息\N{\fs14}Repeating this buIIetin from the coastguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.21,0:30:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找“海草”号\N{\fs14}Be on the Iookout for the Sea Grass -
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.46,0:30:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘30英尺长的拖船\N{\fs14}a thirty-foot trawIer
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.34,0:30:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,最后踪迹位于Spivey Point东约15海里处.\N{\fs14}Iast seen approximateIy 1 5 miIes east of Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.84,0:31:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您看到这艘船 请马上通知海岸警卫队.\N{\fs14}If you sight this vesseI, pIease notify the coastguard immediateIy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.82,0:31:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能问你个问题吗？\N{\fs14}Can l ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.32,0:31:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,总是这种情形吗？ 总是各种情形.\N{\fs14}- ls it always like this? - lt's always different.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.99,0:31:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你很担心，是吗？ 是的.\N{\fs14}- You're worried, aren't you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.29,0:31:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你理解的很对.\N{\fs14}She can get real mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.42,0:31:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿.\N{\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我能听完整个讲话下来 而不打呵欠的话就好了.\N{\fs14}lf l can get through the speeches without yawning...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.68,0:31:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-昨晚我就没睡好. -太兴奋了？\N{\fs14}- l couldn't sleep last night. - Too excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.14,0:31:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔昨晚出海没回来.\N{\fs14}Al went out in his boat last night and didn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.15,0:31:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-他到现在也没回来. -威廉夫人!\N{\fs14}- Still isn't back. - Mrs Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.36,0:31:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队说他可能是碰上引擎出了问题\N{\fs14}The coastguard said he might have had engine trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.95,0:31:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让我不要担心. 上周他就抱怨他的那条船.\N{\fs14}They said not to worry. He was complaining about his boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.07,0:32:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,或许您该回家看看. 那是我今天最后一站.\N{\fs14}- You ought to go home. - That's the last place l wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.83,0:32:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚12:00我的狗狂吠不止 一直叫到今早6:00.\N{\fs14}My dog started to bark at twelve last night and didn't stop until six.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.17,0:32:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？ 它就是朝着大海不停的咆哮.\N{\fs14}- What happened? - He was growling at the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思？ 我的狗疯了，决定开始对水吼叫了.\N{\fs14}What does that tell you? My dog goes crazy and decides to bark at the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.47,0:32:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜时分我也听到教堂钟声了\N{\fs14}l heard the church bells at midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.05,0:32:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的汽车警报器失控了，毫无来由的.\N{\fs14}and suddenly my car alarm went off for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.72,0:32:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的吗？ -吵醒了整个街区.\N{\fs14}- Really? - Woke up the whole block.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.10,0:32:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这座小镇在此坐落100年了，从没发生过什么 但是突然某一晚，整个地区都满是怪事.\N{\fs14}Nothing happens for 100 years, then one night, the whole place falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.86,0:32:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔?\N{\fs14}Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.98,0:32:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这条绳子.\N{\fs14}Take this line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.57,0:32:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔! 汤米!\N{\fs14}Al! Tommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.16,0:32:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克!\N{\fs14}Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.91,0:32:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,船舱和驾驶室都没人.\N{\fs14}Cabin and steering house are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.41,0:32:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有人让他们搭船走了呢.\N{\fs14}Maybe somebody picked them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,蒸汽机里有水.\N{\fs14}There's water in the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.17,0:32:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但甲板上却干爽的像啃过的骨头.\N{\fs14}But the deck is dry as a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.62,0:33:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了吧. 我的下一个计划\N{\fs14}There you have it. My next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.95,0:33:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根镇公路墓地的重修.\N{\fs14}Restoration of the Morgantown Road cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.75,0:33:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是有历史意义的. 我们的祖先就埋在这里. -那耗费太大了.\N{\fs14}- lt's historical, our ancestors... - lt'd cost a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.63,0:33:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢？这座小镇会为它的过去而骄傲. .\N{\fs14}So? This town should be proud of its past.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.30,0:33:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要想让人们参与进公益事业中来 就像拔牙一样难.\N{\fs14}But trying to get anyone involved in community affairs is like pulling teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.76,0:33:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最好提前为下个月召开的委员会议做好预算. 好的，夫人.\N{\fs14}- Get estimates ready for the next meeting. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.43,0:33:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我认识的唯一一个 能把“好的，夫人”说成“想要干你”的语气的人.\N{\fs14}You're the only person who can make ''yes, ma'am'' sound like ''screw you''.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.39,0:33:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，夫人.\N{\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.90,0:33:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,做个小小的祈祷吧 希望他不会淹死在那些酒杯里.\N{\fs14}Say a little prayer, asking that he not be in his cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.36,0:33:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是好兆头.\N{\fs14}Not a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.08,0:33:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,马龙神父？\N{\fs14}Father Malone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.09,0:34:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么? 又一个坏兆头.\N{\fs14}- Hello? - Another bad sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.22,0:34:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你继续研究吉凶吧，而我会继续找.\N{\fs14}You try the study and l'll look up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.87,0:34:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-天哪!神夫，对不起 -对不起，威廉夫人.\N{\fs14}- Jesus. Father, l'm sorry. - l'm sorry, Mrs Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.46,0:34:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-威廉夫人-- -你还好吧？\N{\fs14}- Mrs Williams... - Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.63,0:34:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你看样东西.\N{\fs14}l have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.01,0:34:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,十二月9日.\N{\fs14}''December nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚首次会面了布雷克.\N{\fs14}''Met with Blake this evening for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.77,0:35:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他站在阴影里让我看不清他的面孔.\N{\fs14}''He stood in the shadows to prevent me from getting a clear look at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多么卑劣的事情啊.\N{\fs14}''What a vile disease this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.82,0:35:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个恶贯满盈的富人\N{\fs14}''He is a rich man with a cursed condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.66,0:35:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但这阻止不了他继续加强他的地位.\N{\fs14}''But this does not prevent him from trying to better his situation
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.33,0:35:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和他那些殖民军团的同伙们.\N{\fs14}''and that of his comrades at the colony.''
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.52,0:35:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所有仪器都损坏了. -所有的玻璃都碎了.\N{\fs14}Every single gauge is broken. The glass is shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.48,0:35:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-联想起什么了么？ -昨天夜里.\N{\fs14}- Remind you of something? - Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.82,0:35:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的卡车.\N{\fs14}Your truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.33,0:35:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,温度计也碎了.\N{\fs14}Thermometer's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.13,0:35:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,水银柱定在20度上.\N{\fs14}Mercury's stuck at 20 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没进来水，但却进来了可怕的寒冷.\N{\fs14}There's no water got in here but something awful cold did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.76,0:36:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,十二月11日. 布雷克的计划很简单.\N{\fs14}''December 1 1 . Blake's proposition is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.18,0:36:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他想撤离Tanzier岛\N{\fs14}''He wants to move off Tanzier lsland
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.52,0:36:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在北部重新部署整个殖民军团.\N{\fs14}''and relocate the entire colony just north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.48,0:36:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他用一部分财产买了一艘快速帆船\N{\fs14}''He has purchased a clipper ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.61,0:36:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做‘伊丽莎白.丹恩’号\N{\fs14}''called the Elizabeth Dane, with part of his fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.74,0:36:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后请求在此靠岸.\N{\fs14}''and asks only for permission to settle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.70,0:36:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须对这个可怜的人\N{\fs14}''l must balance my feelings of mercy and compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.91,0:36:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,平衡一下我仁慈和怜悯的感情\N{\fs14}''toward this poor man
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.17,0:36:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把我的思路收回来 那些可怜的殖民军团士兵们.\N{\fs14}''with my revulsion at the thought of a leper colony
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.46,0:36:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅在一海里外\N{\fs14}''only a mile distant.''
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.03,0:37:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,锈到墙里去了.\N{\fs14}lt's rusted to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.57,0:37:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,收音机开着的.\N{\fs14}lt was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.08,0:37:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来昨晚他们喝了不少啤酒. 每晚都是.\N{\fs14}- They drank a lot of beer last night. - Every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.09,0:37:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么样？\N{\fs14}What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.21,0:37:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总是一个样. 屋子开始旋转--\N{\fs14}The room always starts spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.55,0:37:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指钓鱼.\N{\fs14}l mean fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你这条滑鱼. 有关钓鱼我只知道\N{\fs14}- You fish. - The only thing l know about fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.60,0:37:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你用了许多蚯蚓.\N{\fs14}is you use a lot of worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咸水.\N{\fs14}Saltwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,两晚前这艘船还是干净的，我亲自检查的.\N{\fs14}She was clean two nights ago, l checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.45,0:37:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在她却像在水里翻了个底朝天.\N{\fs14}and now it's as if she's been turned over in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,四月20日. 我们中的六个人今晚碰面了\N{\fs14}''April 20. The six of us met tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.87,0:37:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,从午夜直到1:00\N{\fs14}''From midnight until one o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.92,0:37:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们设计了布雷克和他的战友们的死亡\N{\fs14}''we planned the death of Blake and his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.21,0:37:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我对自己说， 布雷克的金币 会帮我们重建教堂\N{\fs14}''l tell myself that Blake's gold will allow the church to be built
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.97,0:38:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的小地盘会变成大村镇\N{\fs14}''and our small settlement to become a township
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.68,0:38:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但这并没减轻我的罪恶感\N{\fs14}''but it does not soothe the horror that l feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.31,0:38:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是谋杀的帮凶\N{\fs14}''being an accomplice to murder.''
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.57,0:38:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办？\N{\fs14}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.69,0:38:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等待海岸警卫队到来.\N{\fs14}Wait for the coastguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.28,0:38:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉. 抱歉什么？\N{\fs14}- l'm sorry. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.41,0:38:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你让我搭了你的车，事情就越来越糟.\N{\fs14}Since you picked me up, things have been going wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.37,0:38:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,挂钟被弄破，窗户被打碎 还有昨晚门外的怪客.\N{\fs14}The clock, the windows breaking, the weirdo at the door last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.17,0:38:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-不关你的事儿. -我可不敢肯定.\N{\fs14}- That isn't you. - l'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.63,0:38:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这些事好像是冲着我发生的.\N{\fs14}Things seem to happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.22,0:38:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是霉运.\N{\fs14}l'm bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信运气，无论好坏.\N{\fs14}l don't believe in luck, good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.10,0:38:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我对什么都不太相信\N{\fs14}l don't believe in anything much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.73,0:38:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以前发生过一些事.\N{\fs14}Something did happen once.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.99,0:38:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲是个渔夫.\N{\fs14}My father was a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.45,0:39:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾开拖船去韦特利暗礁附近.\N{\fs14}He ran a trawler out of Whately Reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.74,0:39:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚上，很晚了他才回来，走进来说道\N{\fs14}One night, late, coming back in,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.08,0:39:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他驶离那暗礁很远，快接近Spivey Point了.\N{\fs14}he was off beyond the reef, out near Spivey Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他迎风望去\N{\fs14}he looked the windward
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.84,0:39:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了一艘双桅船，挂着矮帆\N{\fs14}and saw a brig under short sail,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.63,0:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正向他驶来.\N{\fs14}heading right for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.39,0:39:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他赶紧发无线电. 没人回答他.\N{\fs14}He radioed. There was no reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.19,0:39:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,甲板上什么都没有，\N{\fs14}Nothing moved on the deck
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.44,0:39:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但那船照行不误\N{\fs14}but she held her course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.98,0:39:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲和两个伙计上了那艘双桅船--\N{\fs14}My dad and two of his hands, they boarded the brig -
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.36,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“瑞莎.简”号\N{\fs14}the Resa Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.07,0:39:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,船上一个人也没有.\N{\fs14}No one was on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.12,0:39:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,餐桌上还有食物，冒着腾腾热气的咖啡.\N{\fs14}There was food on the table and a hot, steamy cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.33,0:39:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是再往下看，盛着这些的锡杯却锈到了餐桌里.\N{\fs14}but underneath, the tin cup was rusted to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.63,0:39:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然后有东西攫住了父亲的目光.\N{\fs14}And then something caught my father's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.55,0:39:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一枚西班牙金币，\N{\fs14}lt was a gold doubloon,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.68,0:40:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,铸造于1867年.\N{\fs14}minted in Spain, 1867.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.35,0:40:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸捡起了那枚金币，放到胸前的口袋里\N{\fs14}My dad picked it up, put it in the pocket of his jacket,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,然后拉上了拉链.\N{\fs14}zippered it up, came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.10,0:40:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他回到家，给我们讲了这段经历.\N{\fs14}told us the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.73,0:40:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他拉开口袋的拉链，想把那枚金币给我.\N{\fs14}And he unzippered the pocket to give me the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可是却不见了.\N{\fs14}lt was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.70,0:40:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我还是去温哥华吧.\N{\fs14}l think l'll go to Vancouver now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.96,0:40:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,四月21日. 我们做了那件事.\N{\fs14}''April 21st. The deed is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.00,0:40:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷克跟随着我们岸上的假篝火\N{\fs14}''Blake followed our false fire on shore
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.38,0:40:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他的船在Spivey Point附近的礁石上撞成两半\N{\fs14}''and his ship broke apart on the rocks off Spivey Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.51,0:40:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一场神秘的大雾帮了我们 那雾就像天助我也\N{\fs14}''We were aided by an unearthly fog that rolled in, as if heaven-sent,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.43,0:40:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然上帝今晚并没参与我们的行动.\N{\fs14}''although God had no part in our actions tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.40,0:40:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷克的金币明天就到手了\N{\fs14}''Blake's gold will be recovered tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.77,0:40:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿仁慈的主啊，能宽恕我们的所为\N{\fs14}''but may the Lord forgive us for what we have done.''
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.11,0:40:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法再读下去了.\N{\fs14}l couldn't read any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.08,0:41:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖父有他的表达方式.\N{\fs14}Your grandfather had a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.83,0:41:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚的庆典就是如此滑稽.\N{\fs14}Our celebration tonight is a travesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.88,0:41:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是光荣无比的凶手.\N{\fs14}We're honouring murderers.
