Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.00,0:43:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,EST-111-B\N{\fs14}E-S-T one eIeven B,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.04,0:43:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,第二面.\N{\fs14}Cut two,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.30,0:43:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来自世界之巅,传说中的1340\N{\fs14}From the top of the world, fabulous 1340,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.26,0:43:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,kAB, 安东尼湾\N{\fs14}KAB, Antonio Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.35,0:43:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,神父，你在哪里找到的这个？\N{\fs14}Father, where did you find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.10,0:43:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖父把他的罪孽藏在墙里面.\N{\fs14}My grandfather hid his sins in the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.02,0:44:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候发现的？\N{\fs14}When did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.23,0:44:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚，恰好午夜刚过. 有什么区别吗？\N{\fs14}Last night, just after midnight. What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.45,0:44:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那时正是镇子的其他部分大乱之时.\N{\fs14}That's the same time the rest of the town fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也正是那六个阴谋者碰头之时\N{\fs14}The same time the six conspirators met.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.67,0:44:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,距今一百年前. 真的要晚了.\N{\fs14}- 100 years ago. - lt's really getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.80,0:44:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对这件事我们虽想尽力但却无能为力.\N{\fs14}There's not much we can do about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.42,0:44:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚您会致祝词吧，神父？\N{\fs14}Are you going to give the benediction tonight, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.39,0:44:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼湾遭受了诅咒.\N{\fs14}Antonio Bay has a curse on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.60,0:44:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要我们理解成您是在说“不”吗？\N{\fs14}Do we take that as a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.98,0:44:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许也可以反过来理解.\N{\fs14}Maybe it's just as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.69,0:44:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该走了，神父.\N{\fs14}We're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,您还好吧？\N{\fs14}Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.16,0:44:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去打电话给泰登医生，顺便让他开车过来.\N{\fs14}l'm gonna call Dr Thayden and ask him to just drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.54,0:44:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你把这一切看得太严重了.\N{\fs14}l think you're taking this much too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.33,0:44:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都被诅咒了，威廉夫人\N{\fs14}We're all cursed, Mrs Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.84,0:45:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每个人.\N{\fs14}All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.14,0:45:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,1340.\N{\fs14}1340,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.55,0:45:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,kAB.\N{\fs14}KAB,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.72,0:45:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,44.\N{\fs14}44,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,美妙之声\N{\fs14}The smooth sound,
