Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.58,0:45:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚，安东尼湾.\N{\fs14}Antonio Bay, California,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.33,0:45:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,46.\N{\fs14}46,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.92,0:45:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西缠在脖子上，像个信天翁\N{\fs14}Something that one Iives with Iike an aIbatross round the neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.75,0:45:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不. 更像个磨盘\N{\fs14}No, more Iike a millstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.80,0:46:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个钳砣，天降下来.该死的!\N{\fs14}A pIumbing stone, by God, Damn them aII,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.86,0:46:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时又一小时 KAB 新闻与天气.\N{\fs14}Every hour, on the hour, KAB news and weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.32,0:46:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,10.\N{\fs14}10,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.11,0:46:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时又一小时\N{\fs14}Every hour, on the hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.24,0:46:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,KAB 新闻与天气\N{\fs14}KAB news and weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.91,0:46:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B面结束，KAB广告.\N{\fs14}End side two, KAB promos,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.92,0:46:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人怎么可能淹死了但却没沾水？\N{\fs14}How can a man drown and not touch the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.76,0:46:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他的肺里全是水\N{\fs14}He had water in his lungs,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.97,0:46:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴里都是盐水，衣服上布满了海藻.\N{\fs14}saltwater round his mouth, seaweed in his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.60,0:46:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,除非...\N{\fs14}Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.60,0:47:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧？\N{\fs14}You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.86,0:47:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到他的眼睛了吗？\N{\fs14}Did you see his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.78,0:47:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我看到了.\N{\fs14}Yeah, l saw his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.20,0:47:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，接电话.\N{\fs14}Andy, the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了，科布利兹夫人.\N{\fs14}l got it, Mrs Kobritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.42,0:47:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 你在哪里找到的那块木片？\N{\fs14}- Hello. - Where did you get that driftwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.30,0:47:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了呀，妈妈. 今早在海滩上.\N{\fs14}I toId you, it was on the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.63,0:47:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-具体哪里？ -礁石上面.\N{\fs14}- Where? - By the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.38,0:47:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么回事来着？\N{\fs14}What was it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.34,0:47:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它先是一块金币 然后就变成了木片.\N{\fs14}First it was a gold coin, then it turned into the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.26,0:47:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要求你远离那些礁石 不要再在海滩上捡任何东西.\N{\fs14}l want you to stay away from the rocks. Don't pick up anything else off the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.10,0:47:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可它不属于任何人啊. 我知道，宝贝. 好不好？\N{\fs14}- It didn't beIong to anybody, - l know, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.56,0:47:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不希望你再捡别的东西 除非你先过来叫我一起去. 听到没？\N{\fs14}Just don't pick up anything unless you get me first, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.36,0:47:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了.\N{\fs14}OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.48,0:47:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,科布利兹夫人在吗？ 她刚进来.\N{\fs14}- ls Mrs Kobritz there? - She just came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.16,0:48:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开始播音了.\N{\fs14}l have to start the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.78,0:48:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不要离开家里.\N{\fs14}Don't leave the house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.58,0:48:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈. 答应我.\N{\fs14}- Mom. - Promise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.54,0:48:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\N{\fs14}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.21,0:48:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，安迪. 我也爱你，妈妈. 拜拜.\N{\fs14}- l love you, Andy. - Me too, Mom, Bye,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.28,0:48:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的朋友. 这里是史蒂芙.韦恩，您的夜空之灯\N{\fs14}Ahoy, mateys. This is Stevie Wayne, your night-light.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.12,0:48:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚，安东尼湾，KAB电台\N{\fs14}And KAB, Antonio Bay, California,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.08,0:48:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正在向您直播\N{\fs14}is on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.20,0:48:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我已为您准备了几首乐曲，用来庆祝 安东尼湾的100岁生日.\N{\fs14}l've lined up some tunes to help you celebrate the 100th birthday of Antonio Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.92,0:48:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就让我们开始吧.\N{\fs14}So let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.86,0:49:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈要你做什么，安迪？ 没什么.\N{\fs14}- What did your mother want? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.53,0:49:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有什么事儿.\N{\fs14}lt must have been something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.07,0:49:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事儿.\N{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.07,0:49:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,科布利兹夫人 那些云是怎么回事？\N{\fs14}Mrs Kobritz, what are those clouds out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.46,0:49:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显的致命伤,深深刺入双眼\N{\fs14}Evidence of deep, penetrating wounds in each ocular orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.96,0:49:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一直深入到颅腔内部.\N{\fs14}entering into the cranial cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.63,0:49:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,脸上还有锯齿状的伤口...\N{\fs14}Also, jagged lacerations of the face...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.92,0:49:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在这里等么？ 我要和你一起等.\N{\fs14}- You wanna wait out front? - l'd rather wait here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.35,0:49:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,胸腔已经粉碎 肺里灌满液体.\N{\fs14}Thorax has been crushed and the lungs are filled with fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.31,0:50:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谈几句话可以么？\N{\fs14}Talk to you a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.23,0:50:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好吧？ -你和西蒙斯谈过没？\N{\fs14}She gonna be all right? Did you talk to Simms?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.90,0:50:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们在无线电里通过话. 他正从酒窖湾赶回来.\N{\fs14}By radio. He's coming back from Bodega Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.78,0:50:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么？ 每样东西上都生了锈.\N{\fs14}- What happened out there? - There was rust everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.24,0:50:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就好象那艘船已经在那里了很长时间 一直在水里泡着一样.\N{\fs14}Like it had been there a long time, taking on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.16,0:50:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在床铺下面.\N{\fs14}He was down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.33,0:50:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克，他的伤口里布满了海藻 他的肺里满满的\N{\fs14}His wounds are covered with algae, his lungs are full
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.33,0:50:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,指甲里全是淤泥.\N{\fs14}and there's silt under his finger nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.04,0:50:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前我在盐水湖还见过迪克.巴克斯特.\N{\fs14}l saw Dick Baxter three days ago in Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.00,0:50:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他就躺在那屋的解剖台上 像是在水下呆了一个月似的.\N{\fs14}Now he's in there, looking like he's been underwater for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.28,0:50:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得...？ -我来告诉你怎么回事.\N{\fs14}- Do you feel that? - l'll tell you what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.91,0:51:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-只是变冷了. -水变的就像冰一样冷.\N{\fs14}- lt just got cold in here. - The water acts like ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.04,0:51:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,整个尸体需要一年左右才能腐烂\N{\fs14}A body would take a year to decompose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.55,0:51:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果冻的足够冰冷的话时间会更长.\N{\fs14}Longer, if it was deep and cold enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.09,0:51:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是在船上呀. 就在甲板下面.\N{\fs14}But he was on the boat. He was below decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.09,0:51:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不. 迪克.巴克斯特是死在海水里.\N{\fs14}No, Dick Baxter died in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.28,0:51:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得有三个家伙潜水 去Spivey Point那里寻找那条沉船吗？\N{\fs14}Remember those kids that went diving for that old boat off the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.03,0:51:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现了他们，他们在下面待一周了 也许十天.\N{\fs14}We got to 'em, they'd been down for a week, ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.33,0:51:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢向你发誓，这个人的时间更久.\N{\fs14}l swear to you right now, he's been down longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.21,0:52:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs14}Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.45,0:53:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当那艘漂亮的船失事在我们的海岸上时，虽然\N{\fs14}While the wrecking of that beautiful ship upon our coast was, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.41,0:53:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场所有船员的灾难\N{\fs14}a tragedy to those who were in the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.66,0:53:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但也成为了一种契机 促使这个美妙地区的所有人们，\N{\fs14}it was the catalyst that brought together all the people of this wonderful area.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.84,0:53:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们走到一起 他们为安东尼湾起草宪章\N{\fs14}They came together, they formed the charter for Antonio Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.63,0:53:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们根据宪章为议员们投票\N{\fs14}The charter by which you have voted for these councilmen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.93,0:53:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而这些议员们今晚就坐在我的左右.\N{\fs14}who sit on my left and my right tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.18,0:53:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队正在搜寻他们.\N{\fs14}The coastguard's looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.56,0:53:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会地毯式搜索整个区域 所以，说实在的，我们所能做的就是等待.\N{\fs14}They're gonna cover the area pretty good, so all we can do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.11,0:53:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白，郡长.\N{\fs14}l understand, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.32,0:53:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.61,0:53:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了. 下一个该我了.\N{\fs14}l gotta go. l'm up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.70,0:54:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾，威廉夫人.\N{\fs14}l'm so sorry, Mrs Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.33,0:54:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可笑，我满脑子想的竟然是 我的憨狗狗叫了一夜\N{\fs14}lt's funny but all l can think about is my silly dog barking all night
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.63,0:54:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只盼望艾尔能回家来.\N{\fs14}and me just wishing Al would come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.80,0:54:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,唉，我们可不能 让纪念庆典的女主席泪流满面啊，对吧？\N{\fs14}Now we can't have the chairlady of the birthday celebration in tears, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.93,0:54:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还是等一会再去吧.\N{\fs14}You shouldn't go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.85,0:54:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我现在就必须去.\N{\fs14}l think that's exactly what l ought to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.10,0:54:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感激你的帮忙\N{\fs14}l appreciate all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.44,0:54:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不必客气.\N{\fs14}lt's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.40,0:54:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这一首我找了好长时间.\N{\fs14}I searched a Iong time for this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.99,0:55:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们大家还记得它.\N{\fs14}I hope you remember it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.66,0:55:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,百岁快乐，安东尼湾.\N{\fs14}Happy 100th, Antonio Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.96,0:55:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,庆典仪式正在谢尔比广场进行中.\N{\fs14}The ceremonies are under way at SheIby Square
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.00,0:55:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再过大约一小时，将举行盛大的烛光游行.\N{\fs14}and we'II have the candIeIight procession in an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.59,0:55:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果您抓紧时间的话，就可以赶去参加.\N{\fs14}So if you hurry, you can stiII make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.51,0:55:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队今天下午早些时候发现了“海草”号\N{\fs14}The coastguard found the Sea Grass earIier this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.14,0:55:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有进一步传来有关那艘船\N{\fs14}But there's no further word as to the condition of the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.60,0:55:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,以及船员的信息.\N{\fs14}or the men on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.77,0:55:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一有新的讯息传来，我会及时播报给您.\N{\fs14}I'II keep you posted as the news comes in to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.19,0:55:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿没有其他人也在那场大雾中失踪.\N{\fs14}Hope no one eIse gets Iost out there in the fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.36,0:55:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就回来.\N{\fs14}l'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.29,0:55:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- KAB. 你好. 我叫尼克.卡斯特尔.\N{\fs14}- KAB. - Hello. My name's Nick Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,找到“海草”号的人员之一.\N{\fs14}l'm one of the men who found the Sea Grass this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.04,0:55:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉. 我这里没有进一步的消息.\N{\fs14}l'm sorry, l don't have any further word.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.88,0:55:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话来不是因为这个\N{\fs14}That's not what l called about.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.17,0:56:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚在播音中提到了什么关于雾的？\N{\fs14}You just mentioned something now about the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.64,0:56:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，这事听起来有点离奇\N{\fs14}Well, this is gonna sound a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.69,0:56:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚看到了一场大雾,就在远处的海面上.\N{\fs14}l saw the fog last night, out in the ocean, in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.36,0:56:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那雾...发着光芒.\N{\fs14}It was,,,gIowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.99,0:56:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当时看起来风是向东刮的\N{\fs14}The wind seemed to be moving due east
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.20,0:56:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是雾却一直向西移动.\N{\fs14}and the fog just kept moving west.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.41,0:56:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这话听起来像是疯话. 现在不像了.\N{\fs14}- l know it sounds crazy. - Not right now, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.54,0:56:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,昨夜有事情发生.\N{\fs14}Something happened Iast night,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.79,0:56:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时，那场雾飘移过来 整个小镇都乱了套.\N{\fs14}At the same time that fog was moving in, this whole town went unglued.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.79,0:56:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等.\N{\fs14}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.09,0:56:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再为您放上一曲生日祝福的音乐\N{\fs14}l've got some more birthday music for you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.55,0:56:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,并且为您准备了其他的惊喜.\N{\fs14}and a few other surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.47,0:56:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要准备与天气预报员取得联系.\N{\fs14}And I'II be ready to check in with the weatherman,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.85,0:56:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报员也要与你取得联系.\N{\fs14}And the weatherman will be ready to check in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.90,0:57:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-还在吗？ -我在这儿.\N{\fs14}- Hello. - l'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.40,0:57:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事. 这事也许与“海草”号无关.\N{\fs14}There's one other thing. lt may have nothing to do with the Sea Grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.66,0:57:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不，任何事都可能有关.\N{\fs14}No, anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.87,0:57:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子今天早上找到了一块漂流的木片.\N{\fs14}My son found a piece of driftwood this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.96,0:57:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，梅尔. 你怎么样？\N{\fs14}Hey-hey, Mel. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.71,0:57:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你那收音机里的女朋友谈到你了.\N{\fs14}Your girl on the radio's been talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.59,0:57:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里就是要博她开心的.\N{\fs14}l came in tonight to keep her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.01,0:57:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你今晚不值班呀. 因为我爱我的工作.\N{\fs14}- l thought you were off tonight. - l love my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.18,0:57:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，你可以告诉他们关于那个雾带 正从东南移动过来呢.\N{\fs14}Well, you can tell them about that big fog bank moving in the southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.93,0:57:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-往哪儿？ -你自己看吧.\N{\fs14}- Where? - You'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.14,0:57:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了. 明天见.\N{\fs14}l'm on my way. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.27,0:57:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，梅尔. 明天见.\N{\fs14}Yeah, Mel, l'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.49,0:58:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里.\N{\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.84,0:58:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要赶去Spivey Point的灯塔 你要去么？\N{\fs14}l'm going to the lighthouse on Spivey Point. Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.25,0:58:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-走吧.\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.14,0:58:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- KAB. 嗨，甜心!\N{\fs14}- KAB. - Hi, sweetheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.30,0:58:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你去参加庆典了呢.\N{\fs14}l thought you were celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.43,0:58:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你的夜晚我怎么度过.\N{\fs14}l couldn't spend an evening without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.06,0:58:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,30秒后我就挂线. 有什么新消息？\N{\fs14}l'm up in 30 seconds. What's new?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.27,0:58:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,又一个雾带. 在哪？\N{\fs14}- Another fog bank, - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.56,0:58:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,从东南方向的海面上来. 朝向陆地.\N{\fs14}Coming off the ocean, from the southeast, heading inland.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.11,0:58:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就会到达气象站这里，大约10分钟.\N{\fs14}Should be here in five, ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.20,0:58:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,丹，别挂线.\N{\fs14}Dan, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.07,0:58:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一条特别气象通知.\N{\fs14}l have a special weather bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.99,0:58:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“三村”气象站报告说沿东南海岸方向\N{\fs14}The tri-county weather station reports a fog bank
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.99,0:58:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有一雾带正在移动过来\N{\fs14}moving southeast along the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.12,0:58:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请气象站有关人士注意\N{\fs14}For whoever's interested, that's the weather station.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.08,0:58:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,重复播报 沿东南海岸方向，有一雾带正在移动过来\N{\fs14}Repeating, the fog bank is moving southwest aIong the coast,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.05,0:59:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝老拉塞尔路气象站移动.\N{\fs14}toward the weather station on OId RusseIIviIIe Road,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.51,0:59:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,丹，你还在吗? 我在.\N{\fs14}- Dan, are you still there? - l'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.22,0:59:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚听起来有些不同\N{\fs14}You sound different tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.93,0:59:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎有些激动. 我在照常播音，没别的.\N{\fs14}- Kind of intense, - l just feel like talking, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.69,0:59:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你不喜欢打电话 因为整天对着话筒播报.\N{\fs14}But you don't taIk on the teIephone because you taIk on the radio,,,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.03,0:59:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那雾到哪里了？\N{\fs14}Where's the fog now?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.78,0:59:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻应该就在我的门外了.\N{\fs14}Should be right outside my door now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.49,0:59:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等. 我有点事情要做.\N{\fs14}Hold on, l'm gonna try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.00,0:59:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到它.\N{\fs14}l can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.37,0:59:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我们的约定呢？ 你见过雾的，你一生都能见到雾.\N{\fs14}What's the big deal? You've seen fog once, you've seen it for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.88,0:59:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这场雾有所不同. 它会发光\N{\fs14}There's something different about this fog. lt glows.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.96,0:59:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不出有什么东西吗？ 发光？\N{\fs14}- Can't you see anything yet? - Glows?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.18,0:59:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了. 你一直疲于奔命\N{\fs14}l get it, you take something to keep you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.26,0:59:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有时候感觉有些失常？\N{\fs14}Does it make you feel a little weird sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.14,1:00:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.89,1:00:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,灯灭了.\N{\fs14}The lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.15,1:00:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都一团糟.\N{\fs14}Everything's going crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.15,1:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,气压计下降，温度计回落.\N{\fs14}Barometer's falling, temperature's dropping.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.82,1:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？ 该死的怎么回事？\N{\fs14}- What is it? - What the hell's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.15,1:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？发生什么了？\N{\fs14}What is it? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.11,1:00:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了？\N{\fs14}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.70,1:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,透过窗子有东西在发光.\N{\fs14}Someone's shining a light at the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.99,1:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说. 稍等，甜心.\N{\fs14}- Listen to me, - Hold on, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.29,1:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去看看是怎么回事.\N{\fs14}l wanna check this out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.46,1:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别离开电话!\N{\fs14}Stay on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.47,1:00:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在开玩笑.\N{\fs14}This has gotta be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.23,1:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在前门那里 在开一个蠢笨的玩笑.\N{\fs14}Someone's at the front door, playing a stupid joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.40,1:00:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁 看来是不喜欢到我家去找我，反而来这里.\N{\fs14}And whoever it is, they ain't gonna like finding me home.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.90,1:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开门那里!\N{\fs14}Stay away from the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.17,1:01:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.80,1:01:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\fs14}Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.63,1:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知哪个混蛋喝多了 来搅和咱们的百年庆典\N{\fs14}Some asshole is taking this 100-year-old business too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.39,1:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们所有\N{\fs14}And so all of us,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.27,1:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,住在安东尼湾的人今天\N{\fs14}living here in Antonio Bay today,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.81,1:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都亏欠一份感激\N{\fs14}owe a great debt of gratitude
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.73,1:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为一百年前来到这里的男人女人们\N{\fs14}to those men and women a hundred years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.19,1:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们的奋斗和牺牲\N{\fs14}who struggled and sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.36,1:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,换来了这座小镇的繁荣，才有今天的面貌.\N{\fs14}to make this town grow into what it is today.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.11,1:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到我们来继承他们的精神.\N{\fs14}And it is up to us to keep their kind of spirit alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.46,1:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急播报.\N{\fs14}l have an urgent bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.25,1:02:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,请大卫.西蒙斯郡长马上联系KAB广播电台.\N{\fs14}Will Sheriff Simms please contact KAB radio immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.88,1:02:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,联系电话：555-2131. 这是紧急情况.\N{\fs14}The number is 555 2131 . This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.18,1:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须更加倍的努力与合作.\N{\fs14}So we must redouble our efforts, work together.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.47,1:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一个有生机、有活力的团体. 并且我说，我们一定要一如既往.\N{\fs14}We have a vital, thriving community and l say we have to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.15,1:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是紧急情况.\N{\fs14}This is an emergency,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.86,1:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大卫.西蒙斯郡长，请马上联系KAB.\N{\fs14}Sheriff David Simms, pIease contact KAB immediateIy,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.48,1:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,555-2131. 这是紧急情况.\N{\fs14}555 2131, This is an emergency,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.20,1:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,HeIIo.\N{\fs14}Hello,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.71,1:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.75,1:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,西蒙斯郡长？\N{\fs14}Sheriff Simms?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.67,1:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，在我们即将 为雕像揭幕之际\N{\fs14}As we make our way for the presentation of the statue,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.80,1:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们应该牢牢记住 今夜的重大意义\N{\fs14}we should all keep in mind the significance of this night,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.22,1:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对每个安东尼湾的公民而言的.\N{\fs14}for every citizen of Antonio Bay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.19,1:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都应该依次走向雕像.\N{\fs14}We should all proceed over to the statue.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.56,1:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,列成一排. 不要推搡.慢慢来.\N{\fs14}Single file. Don't push. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.68,1:05:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发动啊!\N{\fs14}Start!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.89,1:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,求你快发动啊!\N{\fs14}Please start!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.02,1:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么灯都灭了呢？\N{\fs14}Why did all the lights go out?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.23,1:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是某条线路出故障了\N{\fs14}One of the lines are probably down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.86,1:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,通常很快他们就会修好的.\N{\fs14}They usually take care of these things right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.48,1:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉是另有原因的.\N{\fs14}l think it's kinda neat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.04,1:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.63,1:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恩？\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.64,1:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那又是什么？\N{\fs14}What's that, now?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.15,1:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,发动啊!\N{\fs14}Start!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.49,1:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，快离开房子!\N{\fs14}Andy, get out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.54,1:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,科布利兹夫人，快带他离开房子！拜托啦！快跑！\N{\fs14}Mrs Kobritz, get him out of the house, please, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.50,1:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们最好把窗子都关上 你卧室的窗子关了吗？\N{\fs14}We'd better close the windows. Are your bedroom windows closed?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.63,1:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看.\N{\fs14}l'll go see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.84,1:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.72,1:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有人听到我吗？我儿子处境危险!\N{\fs14}Someone listen to me. My son is trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.31,1:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,白色海滩路887号! 我儿子处在大雾的危险中! 快离开房子! 快跑!\N{\fs14}887, White Beach Lane. My son is trapped by the fog. Get out! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.86,1:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇! 快看哪!\N{\fs14}Wow! Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.61,1:07:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,窗户都关上了吗？ 是的，夫人.\N{\fs14}- Are your windows all closed? - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.28,1:07:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈的卧室呢？\N{\fs14}l wonder about your mother's bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.58,1:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊，快来人啊! 我儿子被困住了!\N{\fs14}Please, someone, my son is trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.21,1:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，快跑! 跑呀!\N{\fs14}Andy, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.38,1:07:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,科布利兹夫人，快跑!\N{\fs14}Mrs Kobritz, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.68,1:07:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你回到你房间里去. 我觉得我应该呆在这里.\N{\fs14}- l want you to go to your room. - l think l should stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.93,1:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-马上.\N{\fs14}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.62,1:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快去你的房间. 我想看看到底是谁.\N{\fs14}- Go to your room. - l wanna see who it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.29,1:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我再呆两秒不行吗？\N{\fs14}- No. - Can't l stay for two more seconds?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.21,1:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我回房间.\N{\fs14}OK, l'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.20,1:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,救命. 我儿子被困住了!\N{\fs14}Please, my son is trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.03,1:08:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,白色海滩路887号.\N{\fs14}887, White Beach Lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.62,1:08:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁能去白色海滩路887号？\N{\fs14}Someone get to 887, White Beach Lane,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.32,1:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子被困住了! 快把他从雾里弄出来!\N{\fs14}My son is trapped, Get out of the fog,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.85,1:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，有人吗!\N{\fs14}PIease, someone!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.10,1:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子处境危险!\N{\fs14}My son is trapped!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.27,1:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...白色海滩路.\N{\fs14},, White Beach Lane,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.61,1:09:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧! 快点出来，快!\N{\fs14}Come on, get out of there, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.41,1:09:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，快跑!\N{\fs14}Andy, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.50,1:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跑呀!\N{\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.71,1:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快点! 快! 快!\N{\fs14}- Come on. - Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.10,1:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊! 别催. 别乱动. 尽量平稳才能出去.\N{\fs14}- Come on. - Easy. Don't pop it. Ease it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.31,1:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，天哪.\N{\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.57,1:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快点啊\N{\fs14}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.07,1:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会行的.会行的.\N{\fs14}lt'll go, it'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.49,1:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,倒车! 倒车! 快!\N{\fs14}- Reverse! Reverse! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊，倒车! 倒!\N{\fs14}Come on! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.24,1:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芙.韦恩为您播音最后二十分钟.\N{\fs14}We've been waiting 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.37,1:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为现在时间已经差不多了.\N{\fs14}l think it's best we call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.95,1:10:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,再给五分钟 每个人都会瞻仰到雕像.\N{\fs14}ln five minutes, everyone will have seen the statue.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.08,1:10:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，但是让他们尽可能快些走过.\N{\fs14}All right. Let's get them through quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.88,1:10:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你该回家是个不错的主意，凯西.\N{\fs14}Probably be a good idea if you went home, Kathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.50,1:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把这里封锁起来. 我要呆到全部结束.\N{\fs14}- We can close up here. - l should see it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.76,1:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没什么要您做的了 让我陪您回家吧.\N{\fs14}There's nothing more to do here. Let me take you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.14,1:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点讨厌，不过你是对的.\N{\fs14}A little annoying but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.68,1:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-你送我回去么？ -是的，夫人.\N{\fs14}- Would you please take me? - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.02,1:11:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-明早我会给你打电话. -谢谢.\N{\fs14}- l'll call you tomorrow. - OK. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.36,1:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你到底能不能听到我\N{\fs14}l don't even know if you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.23,1:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉，我不能去和你在一起 我不能离开这里.\N{\fs14}l'm sorry that l didn't come for you, that l wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.78,1:11:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要明白\N{\fs14}Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.53,1:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须呆在这里.\N{\fs14}l have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.71,1:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那雾刚刚离开海滩\N{\fs14}The fog is moving inland,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.30,1:11:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,正往陆地上漂去\N{\fs14}away from the beach,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.76,1:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着安东尼湾.\N{\fs14}towards Antonio Bay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.21,1:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正在兵工厂上空.\N{\fs14}It's by the armoury,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.88,1:12:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了那个兵工厂的名字了.\N{\fs14}I can't remember the name of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.01,1:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该是栗子兵工厂.\N{\fs14}I think it's Chestnut,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.35,1:12:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想要听音乐吗？\N{\fs14}Feel like listening to some music?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.56,1:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.89,1:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,移动的越来越快了. 到摄政街了.到小房子之路的尽头了.\N{\fs14}It's moving faster now, up Regent Avenue, up to the end of SmaIIhouse Road,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.27,1:12:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?\N{\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.24,1:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是侵袭了小镇的外围镇郊.\N{\fs14}It's just hitting the outskirts of town,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.28,1:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,中央大街.\N{\fs14}Broad Street,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.49,1:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,陶土大街.\N{\fs14}CIay Street,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.73,1:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝第10大街漂去.\N{\fs14}It's moving down Tenth Street,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.77,1:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请回到屋内，锁好门. 关好窗子.\N{\fs14}Get inside and Iock your doors, CIose your windows,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.23,1:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雾中有什么东西.\N{\fs14}There's something in the fog,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.99,1:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您在小镇的南部，请往北部去.\N{\fs14}lf you're on the south side of town, go north.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.70,1:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,远离那雾.\N{\fs14}Stay away from the fog.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.83,1:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从Richardsville Pike到Beacon Hill 是唯一能看清的道路.\N{\fs14}RichardsviIIe Pike up to Beacon HiII is the onIy cIear road,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.96,1:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一直到教堂. 如果你能离开小镇，请赶往老教堂.\N{\fs14}Up to the church, If you can get out of town, get to the oId church,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.31,1:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在整个小镇在101里程处被分成两半.\N{\fs14}Now the junction at 101 is cut off,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.77,1:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能离开小镇，请赶往老教堂.\N{\fs14}If you can get out of town, get to the oId church,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.27,1:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是唯一可以去的地方.\N{\fs14}It's the onIy pIace Ieft to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.69,1:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快去Beacon Hill的老教堂.\N{\fs14}Get to the oId church on Beacon HiII,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.03,1:14:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-把我们的镇分开了？ -那东西在哪里？\N{\fs14}- lt cut us off. - Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.79,1:14:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-就在我们身后. -快点，进去.\N{\fs14}- Right behind us, in the driveway. - Quick. lnside.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.54,1:14:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快点. 快.\N{\fs14}- Come on. - Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.21,1:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,马龙神父？\N{\fs14}Father Malone?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.38,1:14:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗? 这里有地下室或者地窖吗？\N{\fs14}- Are you all right? - ls there a basement?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.92,1:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们藏不多久的. -那也要试试!\N{\fs14}- Can't hide. - We have to try.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.09,1:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我们跑到哪里，它都会找到我们的.\N{\fs14}No matter where we go, it will find us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.43,1:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有地下室或者地窖吗？ 我了解过这里\N{\fs14}- ls there a basement? - There's a study.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.89,1:14:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你们带路，快点\N{\fs14}l'll show you the way. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.27,1:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快. 快，给我.\N{\fs14}- Hurry. - Come on. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.09,1:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大雾正在横扫内地.\N{\fs14}The fog is sweeping inland.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.63,1:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一堵墙横过小镇的东部.\N{\fs14}lt's almost like a wall across the east end of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.95,1:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷克和他的伙伴们来找我们啦. -布雷克是谁？\N{\fs14}- Blake's come for us. - Who's Blake?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.08,1:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-日记里记载着. -什么日记？\N{\fs14}- lt's in a journal. - What journal?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.12,1:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-我也不知道. -我们被诅咒了.\N{\fs14}- l don't know. Where is it? - We're cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.46,1:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-你们在说什么？ 日记\N{\fs14}- What are you saying? - The journal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.58,1:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-在那里.\N{\fs14}lt's in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.67,1:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在窗子上？ -现在它对我们没什么用处.\N{\fs14}- By the window? - lt can do us no good now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.18,1:15:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在我们只有这个. 不管发生什么，尽管锁上门.\N{\fs14}lt's all we've got. lf anything happens, lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.80,1:16:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去. 关上门.\N{\fs14}Get back. Shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.01,1:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,“六个人必须死.” “海草”号上的三个人.\N{\fs14}- Six must die... - The three men on the Sea Grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.55,1:16:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,加上气象预报员是四个. -科布利兹夫人.\N{\fs14}- The weather man is four. - Mrs Kobritz.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.76,1:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,五个了 再有我们中的一个，就是六个了.\N{\fs14}- Five. - And one of us makes six.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.18,1:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他们的要求. 为了找到最初那六个阴谋者.\N{\fs14}That's what they want - the six original conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.48,1:16:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一定还有什么东西! 他们要的是我\N{\fs14}- There must be something here. - They want me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.98,1:16:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是第六个! 他们为什么想要你？\N{\fs14}- l am the sixth. - Why would they want you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.86,1:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,复活亡灵是有可能的\N{\fs14}''Were it possible to raise the dead,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.15,1:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把布雷克的财宝完整无缺的还给他\N{\fs14}''l would return Blake's fortune to him intact,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.57,1:17:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把建造这些墙壁的钱攒起来\N{\fs14}''save the money spent on these walls that hide it.''
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.32,1:17:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的同谋们认为 有人偷了大家的财宝\N{\fs14}''My fellow conspirators believe that the fortune was stolen from them
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.87,1:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而事实上，我就是那个小偷 而神的庙宇，就是金子的墓穴\N{\fs14}''when, in fact, l am the thief and God's temple is the tomb of gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.96,1:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那个小偷，而神的庙宇\N{\fs14}''l am the thief and God's temple is the tomb...''
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.88,1:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等等. 把那个拿下来\N{\fs14}Wait. Get rid of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.80,1:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别档着!\N{\fs14}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.82,1:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-帮我一下. 呆在那儿.\N{\fs14}- Give me a hand. - Stay over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.18,1:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,金子.\N{\fs14}Gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.11,1:18:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他把金子熔化制成这个.\N{\fs14}He melted down the gold into this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.72,1:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别去那里!\N{\fs14}Don't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.30,1:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷克，你的金子在我这里.\N{\fs14}Blake, l have your gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.51,1:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的金子\N{\fs14}This is your gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.72,1:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖父偷了你的.\N{\fs14}My grandfather stole it from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.47,1:20:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是必须承担一切的那个人.\N{\fs14}l'm the one who must answer for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.41,1:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是第六个同谋.\N{\fs14}l'm the sixth conspirator.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.95,1:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是马龙神父.\N{\fs14}l'm Father Malone.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.41,1:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抓我吧.\N{\fs14}Take me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.09,1:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,马龙神父!\N{\fs14}Father Malone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.90,1:24:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了.\N{\fs14}lt's going away.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.97,1:25:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知今晚安东尼湾到底发生了什么.\N{\fs14}l don't know what happened to Antonio Bay tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.64,1:25:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雾里出来了什么东西\N{\fs14}Something came out of the fog
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.72,1:25:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并且要毁灭我们.\N{\fs14}and tried to destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.77,1:25:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,突然一瞬间，它又消失了.\N{\fs14}ln one moment, it vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.69,1:25:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是别的事情，而不是这场噩梦的话\N{\fs14}But if this has been anything but a nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.02,1:25:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们醒来没有发现我们身处险境的话\N{\fs14}and if we don't wake up to find ourselves safe in our beds,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.53,1:25:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们迟早会再经历的.\N{\fs14}it could come again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.90,1:25:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在此说给那些沉睡在海底但能听到我声音的人们\N{\fs14}To the ships at sea who can hear my voice,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.53,1:25:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那些穿过深深的海水望向黑暗的人们.\N{\fs14}look across the water, into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.08,1:25:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找那场雾的人们.\N{\fs14}Look for the fog.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.57,1:26:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不凑够六个，布雷克？\N{\fs14}Why not six, Blake?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.53,1:26:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不是我？\N{\fs14}Why not me?

